            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">不知道为何家里会有这“套”书……没有毒害我的心灵……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="925452949">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-925452949" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-925452949" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="925452949">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pipichen/">翻·墙陈</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-07-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">是不是翻译问题，语言好老旧。对武则天杀婴嫁祸王萧的历史迷案分析很有道理</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="166373838">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-166373838" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-166373838" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="166373838">有用</a>
