    <div class="main review-item" id="1425493">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1425493/" class="title-link">武则天日本行</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1425493"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1206412/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1206412-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1206412/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沈公子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-07-01"
      class="main-meta">2008-07-01 13:05:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1425493_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  多年前在福州路买到这部书，如获至宝。作者对唐朝典故和社会生活、经济政治的深刻体认，以及由此阐发的故事背景，都让作为中国历史爱好者的我叹为观止。相比其他对女皇帝揣测、讥讽或辩护的书籍，这部书是我看过的最好的女皇传记。中国历史学家和小说家，宁不愧死？

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
